Name: Team Rewards
Description: Additional rewards that may be obtained when participating in multiplayer gameplay, including non-bound precious items that can be listed for trade. \n Completing Challenges in Unstable Space in multiplayer mode grants a chance to receive extra non-bound rewards, such as Reforge Stone Lv.60 (unbound), Starforge Crystal Lv.1 (unbound) and Starforge Crystal Lv.2 (unbound).
